-- Lynxiz --

Lynxiz slides through the underbrush, and manoevers her way until 
she arrives at the coordinates. Her optics move over the base 
slowly, and her instincts tell her something is wrong, but she 
shrugs them off. 

She opens a commlink to the base, "Panthero, this is Lynxiz, I've 
just arrived. I'm interested in learning more about this faction." 
Her tail swishes, and she sits down beside a tree, not far from the 
north side of the base.
